A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the 90th anniversary of the Earl and Rachel Smith Strand Theatre; and for other
2 purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Earl and Rachel Smith Strand Theatre has proudly stood for 90 years as a
4 cultural landmark and architectural gem on the Historic Marietta Square, enriching the lives
5 of generations of Georgians; and
6 WHEREAS, the Strand first opened its doors on September 24, 1935, as a grand Art Deco
7 movie palace with seating for over 1,000 guests, ushering in a new era of cinematic
8 entertainment for Cobb County and the surrounding region; and
9 WHEREAS, throughout the decades, the Strand has evolved into a treasured gathering place
10 for the community, offering entertainment, fellowship, and a sense of shared heritage for
11 audiences of all ages; and
12 WHEREAS, thanks to the passion and persistence of the "Friends of the Strand" and the
13 generosity of countless donors, the theatre was beautifully restored and reopened in 2009,
14 blending historical preservation with a renewed purpose as a vibrant venue for live
15 performances, classic films, and special events; and
